{"metadata":{"symbolKind":"protocol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"PaymentIntentProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:@M@Airwallex@objc(pl)PaymentIntentProvider","modules":[{"name":"Airwallex"}],"title":"PaymentIntentProvider","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"PaymentIntentProvider"}],"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Protocol"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/airwallex\/paymentintentprovider"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]},{"paths":["\/documentation\/airwallex\/paymentintentprovider"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.cocoapods.Airwallex\/documentation\/Airwallex"]]},"topicSections":[{"title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/org.cocoapods.Airwallex\/documentation\/Airwallex\/PaymentIntentProvider\/amount","doc:\/\/org.cocoapods.Airwallex\/documentation\/Airwallex\/PaymentIntentProvider\/currency","doc:\/\/org.cocoapods.Airwallex\/documentation\/Airwallex\/PaymentIntentProvider\/customerId"],"anchor":"Instance-Properties","generated":true},{"title":"Instance Methods","identifiers":["doc:\/\/org.cocoapods.Airwallex\/documentation\/Airwallex\/PaymentIntentProvider\/createPaymentIntent()"],"anchor":"Instance-Methods","generated":true}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/org.cocoapods.Airwallex\/documentation\/Airwallex\/PaymentIntentProvider"},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A protocol for providing payment intents on-demand during the payment flow."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@objc"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"PaymentIntentProvider"}],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaymentIntentProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" enables delayed payment intent creation, allowing you to defer"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the creation of a payment intent until just before payment confirmation or when it is required."}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When using "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Session"},{"type":"text","text":" with a payment intent provider instead of a pre-created intent,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the SDK will call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"createPaymentIntent()"},{"type":"text","text":" asynchronously when needed. The provider"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"must also supply the basic payment information (amount, currency, customerId) synchronously."}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Usage Example","anchor":"Usage-Example"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class MyPaymentIntentProvider: NSObject, PaymentIntentProvider {","    let amount: NSDecimalNumber = NSDecimalNumber(string: \"99.99\")","    let currency: String = \"USD\"","    let customerId: String? = \"customer_123\"","","    func createPaymentIntent() async throws -> AWXPaymentIntent {","        \/\/ Call your backend to create the payment intent","        let response = try await MyBackendAPI.createPaymentIntent(","            amount: amount.decimalValue,","            currency: currency,","            customerId: customerId","        )","        return response.paymentIntent","    }","}","","\/\/ Use with Session","let provider = MyPaymentIntentProvider()","let session = Session(","    paymentIntentProvider: provider,","    countryCode: \"US\",","    returnURL: \"myapp:\/\/payment\/return\"",")"]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Important Notes","anchor":"Important-Notes"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"amount"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"currency"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"customerId"},{"type":"text","text":" properties must return values immediately (they cannot be async)"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The values returned by "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"amount"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"currency"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"customerId"},{"type":"text","text":" must match the values"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AWXPaymentIntent"},{"type":"text","text":" returned by "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"createPaymentIntent()"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"amount"},{"type":"text","text":" should be zero for recurring-only payments (no immediate charge)"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"createPaymentIntent()"},{"type":"text","text":" method will only be called once, and the result is cached"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"createPaymentIntent()"},{"type":"text","text":" throws an error, the payment flow will fail"}]}]}]},{"type":"aside","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":""},{"code":"Session","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"code":"AWXPaymentIntent","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"See Also","style":"note"}]}],"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://org.cocoapods.Airwallex/documentation/Airwallex/PaymentIntentProvider/customerId":{"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"customerId"}],"url":"\/documentation\/airw